---
// Hero component
---

<section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center px-6 py-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-950 via-gray-900 to-gray-950">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Logo/Icon -->
    <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="w-24 h-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-green-400 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shadow-2xl">
          <div class="text-white text-3xl font-bold">&lt;/&gt;</div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-400 to-green-300 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="w-4 h-4 bg-white rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Headline -->
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-green-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent" style="line-height: 1.2;">
      Ruta Express para Programadores
    </h1>
    
    <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white mb-8">
      Ten&eacute; claridad total en 30 minutos para empezar a programar sin frustrarte
    </h2>

    <!-- Subheadline -->
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Descarg&aacute; esta hoja de ruta lista para usar y evit&aacute; perder meses viendo videos que no te llevan a ning&uacute;n lado. 
      <span class="text-green-400 font-semibold">Ideal para personas que empiezan desde cero.</span>
    </p>

    <!-- Benefits Bullets -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex items-center text-left">
        <img src="/check-mark-button.png" alt="Check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-3">
        <span class="text-white">Eleg&iacute; el lenguaje ideal para vos</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center text-left">
        <img src="/check-mark-button.png" alt="Check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-3">
        <span class="text-white">Sab&eacute; qu&eacute; hacer semana a semana</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center text-left">
        <img src="/check-mark-button.png" alt="Check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-3">
        <span class="text-white">Evit&aacute; errores comunes de principiantes</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center text-left">
        <img src="/check-mark-button.png" alt="Check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-3">
        <span class="text-white">Empez&aacute; hoy con foco y confianza</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Price and CTA -->
    <div class="mb-8">
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-green-400 mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
        <img src="/backhand-index-pointing-right.png" alt="Pointing right" class="w-8 h-8 mr-2">
        Llevate la gu&iacute;a hoy por solo $17
      </p>
      <a 
        href="#comprar" 
        class="inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-green-500 hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-xl font-bold transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg"
      >
        COMPRAR AHORA
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Product Mockup Placeholder -->
    <div class="mt-12 max-w-md mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-700">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="flex space-x-2">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div class="h-4 bg-gray-700 rounded w-3/4"></div>
          <div class="h-4 bg-gray-700 rounded w-1/2"></div>
          <div class="h-4 bg-gray-700 rounded w-5/6"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 